B.a10=new A.aL("\u201cDr. Hannah Sofian and Sayed Aziz, this is the Smart RVM mobile supervisor app. It receives real-time telemetry from Firebase Cloud Firestore, which is dynamically updated by the ESP32 network bridge connected to the Arduino Mega co-processor. When a PET bottle is successfully classified, the accepted count increases and the app records the transaction. If a metal can is inserted, the inductive signature triggers Deflector Gate Deflection and increments the rejected tally. Critical alarms (like storage bin saturation or offline statuses) are immediately flagged on the telemetry dashboard and trigger local push notifications.\u201d",null,B.Yt,null,null,null,null,null,null,null)
